name: Coconut Minis Vanilla Sandwich Cake
author: So Delicious® Dairy Free
summary: Life doesn't always go as planned. Sometimes, fun has to happen on short notice. This gorgeous dairy-free dessert tastes astoundingly good and comes together in a matter of minutes. Your kids can even help you make it! How fun is that?
ingredients: 12  So Delicious® Coconut Milk Minis Vanilla Sandwiches
1 (9 ounce) tub So Delicious® Dairy Free CocoWhip
½ cup berries (raspberries, blackberries, strawberries or cherries)
Drizzle of Jen's Zen vegan chocolate sauce
directions: Start by assembling 6 sandwiches side by side
Top with CocoWhip and layer with another 6 sandwiches: repeat
Top with raspberries, blackberries, strawberries or cherries
Finish with a drizzle of Jen's Zen vegan chocolate sauce
